{"tid":1869170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"邊條撚屌話手持口罩有閪屌㗎","createTime":"2020-02-08T04:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:42:59.000Z","uid":254923,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce8b4342d2d6955cbc15caa6c4de358fa952f093","tid":1869170,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"早幾日喺連登睇到話有口罩就有閪屌 特登同老細請咗日假同啲廢佬排通宵終於買到兩盒口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住可以結束我25年嘅處男生涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n思前想後咗幾日 終於今日就的起心肝本住幫到人同時我又破到處嘅精神出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左半日MK終於比我搵到個無戴口罩嘅靚女<br />\n咁我就梗係唔放過啦 心諗機會終於黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住靚女都好等口罩洗 我就拎住盒口罩直接走過去問：一盒幾多Q？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚女：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能佢有啲怕醜我就再直接啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：口罩啊 屌閪啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女呆咗一呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢隔離條仔打咗我一身 連盒口罩都搶撚埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌撚哂你班連登仔老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb1f044ac23b1d9bdecec9c0d77c29c875191bd","tid":1869170,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"條女自己有口罩緊係唔撚理你啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"48c9f496600858bf5b80b7a27002d4bc698dfa55","tid":1869170,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb1f044ac23b1d9bdecec9c0d77c29c875191bd","tid":1869170,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"條女自己有口罩緊係唔撚理你啦傻鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"就係見佢無戴我先敢問咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa44e2563f2aa3f962249e0913cae3e454c977f","tid":1869170,"uid":214644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"可能條女本身已經想應承你，只係因為條仔喺佢側邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油，下次搵過第個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}